T1	Participants 56 109	total hip replacement: a randomized prospective study
T2	Participants 456 601	From 2004 to 2008, 81 patients seeking elective THRs were randomly assigned into a standard rehabilitation group or an early rehabilitation group
T3	Participants 607 802	standard group included restrictions to avoid hip flexion >90 degrees and avoidance of riding in a car for the first postoperative month. The early group had no flexion or car riding restrictions
T4	Participants 804 891	Forty-three patients were in the standard group and 38 patients were in the early group
T5	Participants 904 963	no significant demographic differences between the 2 groups
